iliar spirits"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Lev:20:7","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Consecrate yourselves and be holy, for I am the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" your God. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Lev:20:8","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Keep my statutes and do them; I am the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" who sets you apart."}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Lev:20:9","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"“If anyone curses his father or mother, he must be put to death. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ex 21:17","book":"Exo","chapter":21,"verse":17,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Dt 21:18","book":"Deu","chapter":21,"verse":18,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Dt 27:16","book":"Deu","chapter":27,"verse":16,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Pr 20:20","book":"Pro","chapter":20,"verse":20,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Pr 30:11","book":"Pro","chapter":30,"verse":11,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 15:4","book":"Mat","chapter":15,"verse":4,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mk 7:10","book":"Mrk","chapter":7,"verse":10,"letter":"g"},{"kind":"text","text":" He has cursed his father or mother; his death is his own fault. "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Lit his blood on him"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ex 21:17","book":"Exo","chapter":21,"verse":17},{"label":"Dt 21:18","book":"Deu","chapter":21,"verse":18},{"label":"Dt 27:16","book":"Deu","chapter":27,"verse":16},{"label":"Pr 20:20","book":"Pro","chapter":20,"verse":20},{"label":"Pr 30:11","book":"Pro","chapter":30,"verse":11},{"label":"Mt 15:4","book":"Mat","chapter":15,"verse":4},{"label":"Mk 7:10","book":"Mrk","chapter":7,"verse":10}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Lit his blood on him"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Lev:20:10","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"“If a man commits adultery "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ex 20:14","book":"Exo","chapter":20,"verse":14,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Dt 5:18","book":"Deu","chapter":5,"verse":18,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Dt 22:22","book":"Deu","chapter":22,"verse":22,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Dt 31:16","book":"Deu","chapter":31,"verse":16,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Pr 6:32","book":"Pro","chapter":6,"verse":32,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mal 3:5","book":"Mal","chapter":3,"verse":5,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 5:27–28","book":"Mat","chapter":5,"verse":27,"letter":"g"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 5:32","book":"Mat","chapter":5,"verse":32,"letter":"h"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 19:9","book":"Mat","chapter":19,"verse":9,"letter":"i"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 19:18","book":"Mat","chapter":19,"verse":18,"letter":"j"},{"kind":"text","text":" with a married woman —if he commits adultery with his neighbor’s wife —both the adulterer and the adulteress must be put to death. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ex 20:14","book":"Exo","chapter":20,"verse":14},{"label":"Dt 5:18","book":"Deu","chapter":5,"verse":18},{"label":"Dt 22:22","book":"Deu","chapter":22,"verse":22},{"label":"Dt 31:16","book":"Deu","chapter":31,"verse":16},{"label":"Pr 6:32","book":"Pro","chapter":6,"verse":32},{"label":"Mal 3:5","book":"Mal","chapter":3,"verse":5},{"label":"Mt 5:27–28","book":"Mat","chapter":5,"verse":27},{"label":"Mt 5:32","book":"Mat","chapter":5,"verse":32},{"label":"Mt 19:9","book":"Mat","chapter":19,"verse":9},{"label":"Mt 19:18","book":"Mat","chapter":19,"verse":18}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Lev:20:11","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"If a man sleeps with his father’s wife, he has violated the intimacy that belongs to his father. "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Lit has uncovered his father’s nakedness"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lv 18:8","book":"Lev","chapter":18,"verse":8,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Dt 22:30","book":"Deu","chapter":22,"verse":30,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Dt 27:20","book":"Deu","chapter":27,"verse":20,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Co 5:1","book":"1Co","chapter":5,"verse":1,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"text","text":" Both of them must be put to death; their death is their own fault. "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":2,"text":"Lit their blood on them, also in vv. 12,13,16,27"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Lv 18:8","book":"Lev","chapter":18,"verse":8},{"label":"Dt 22:30","book":"Deu","chapter":22,"verse":30},{"label":"Dt 27:20","book":"Deu","chapter":27,"verse":20},{"label":"1Co 5:1","book":"1Co","chapter":5,"verse":1}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Lit has uncovered his father’s nakedness"},{"marker":2,"text":"Lit their blood on them, also in vv. 12,13,16,27"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Lev:20:12","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"If a man sleeps with his daughter-in-law, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gn 38:16","book":"Gen","chapter":38,"verse":16,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lv 18:15","book":"Lev","chapter":18,"verse":15,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ezk 22:11","book":"Ezk","chapter":22,"verse":11,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" both of them must be put to death. They have acted perversely; their death is their own fault. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Gn 38:16","book":"Gen","chapter":38,"verse":16},{"label":"Lv 18:15","book":"Lev","chapter":18,"verse":15},{"label":"Ezk 22:11","book":"Ezk","chapter":22,"verse":11}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Lev:20:13","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"If a man sleeps with a man as with a woman, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gn 19:5","book":"Gen","chapter":19,"verse":5,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" they have both committed a detestable act. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gn 46:34","book":"Gen","chapter":46,"verse":34,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" They must be put to death; their death is their own fault. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Gn 19:5","book":"Gen","chapter":19,"verse":5},{"label":"Gn 46:34","book":"Gen","chapter":46,"verse":34}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Lev:20:14","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"If a man marries "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":3,"text":"Lit takes, also in vv. 17,21"},{"kind":"text","text":" a woman and her mother, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lv 18:17","book":"Lev","chapter":18,"verse":17,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" it is depraved. Both he and they must be burned, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gn 38:24","book":"Gen","chapter":38,"verse":24,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lv 18:22","book":"Lev","chapter":18,"verse":22,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lv 21:9","book":"Lev","chapter":21,"verse":9,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jdg 14:15","book":"Jdg","chapter":14,"verse":15,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rv 17:16","book":"Rev","chapter":17,"verse":16,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"text","text":" so that there will be no depravity among you. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Lv 18:17","book":"Lev","chapter":18,"verse":17},{"label":"Gn 38:24","book":"Gen","chapter":38,"verse":24},{"label":"Lv 18:22","book":"Lev","chapter":18,"verse":22},{"label":"Lv 21:9","book":"Lev","chapter":21,"verse":9},{"label":"Jdg 14:15","book":"Jdg","chapter":14,"verse":15},{"label":"Rv 17:16","book":"Rev","chapter":17,"verse":16}],"footnotes":[{"marker":3,"text":"Lit takes, also in vv. 17,21"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Lev:20:15","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"If a man has sexual intercourse with "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":4,"text":"Lit man gives his emission to"},{"kind":"text","text":" an animal, he must be put to death; you are also to kill the animal. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[{"marker":4,"text":"Lit man gives his emission to"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Lev:20:16","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"If a woman approaches any animal and mates with it, you are to kill the woman and the animal. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ex 22:19","book":"Exo","chapter":22,"verse":19,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" They must be put to death; their death is their own fault. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ex 22:19","book":"Exo","chapter":22,"verse":19}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Lev:20:17","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"If a man marries his sister, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lv 18:13","book":"Lev","chapter":18,"verse":13,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" whether his father’s daughter or his mother’s daughter, and they have sexual relations, "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":5,"text":"Lit and he sees her nakedness and she sees his nakedness"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lv 18:9","book":"Lev","chapter":18,"verse":9,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" it is a disgrace. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lv 19:29","book":"Lev","chapter":19,"verse":29,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" They are to be cut off publicly from their people. He has had sexual intercourse with his sister; he will bear his iniquity. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Lv 18:13","book":"Lev","chapter":18,"verse":13},{"label":"Lv 18:9","book":"Lev","chapter":18,"verse":9},{"label":"Lv 19:29","book":"Lev","chapter":19,"verse":29}],"footnotes":[{"marker":5,"text":"Lit and he sees her nakedness and she sees his nakedness"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Lev:20:18","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"If a man sleeps with a menstruating woman and has sexual intercourse with her, he has exposed the source of her flow, and she has uncovered the source of her blood. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lv 18:19","book":"Lev","chapter":18,"verse":19,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" Both of them are to be cut off from their people. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Lv 18:19","book":"Lev","chapter":18,"verse":19}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Lev:20:19","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"You must not have sexual intercourse with your mother’s sister or your father’s sister, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ex 6:20","book":"Exo","chapter":6,"verse":20,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lv 18:12","book":"Lev","chapter":18,"verse":12,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" for it is exposing one’s own blood relative; both people will bear their iniquity. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ex 6:20","book":"Exo","chapter":6,"verse":20},{"label":"Lv 18:12","book":"Lev","chapter":18,"verse":12}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Lev:20:20","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"If a man sleeps with his aunt, he has violated the intimacy that belongs to his uncle; "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":6,"text":"Lit has uncovered his uncle’s nakedness"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lv 18:14","book":"Lev","chapter":18,"verse":14,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" they will bear their guilt and die childless. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Lv 18:14","book":"Lev","chapter":18,"verse":14}],"footnotes":[{"marker":6,"text":"Lit has uncovered his uncle’s nakedness"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Lev:20:21","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"If a man marries his brother’s wife, it is impurity. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mk 6:18","book":"Mrk","chapter":6,"verse":18,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" He has violated the intimacy that belongs to his brother; "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":7,"text":"Lit has uncovered his brother’s nakedness"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lv 18:16","book":"Lev","chapter":18,"verse":16,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" they will be childless."}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Mk 6:18","book":"Mrk","chapter":6,"verse":18},{"label":"Lv 18:16","book":"Lev","chapter":18,"verse":16}],"footnotes":[{"marker":7,"text":"Lit has uncovered his brother’s nakedness"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Lev:20:22","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"“You are to keep all my statutes and all my ordinances, and do them, so that the land where I am bringing you to live will not vomit you out. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lv 18:25","book":"Lev","chapter":18,"verse":25,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Lv 18:25","book":"Lev","chapter":18,"verse":25}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Lev:20:23","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"You must not follow the statutes of the nations I am driving out before you, for they did all these things, and I abhorred them. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ex 23:24","book":"Exo","chapter":23,"verse":24,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lv 18:3","book":"Lev","chapter":18,"verse":3,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ex 23:24","book":"Exo","chapter":23,"verse":24},{"label":"Lv 18:3","book":"Lev","chapter":18,"verse":3}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Lev:20:24","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"And I promised you: You will inherit their land, since I will give it to you to possess, a land flowing with milk and honey. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ex 3:8","book":"Exo","chapter":3,"verse":8,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ex 13:5","book":"Exo","chapter":13,"verse":5,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Nm 14:8","book":"Num","chapter":14,"verse":8,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Nm 16:13–14","book":"Num","chapter":16,"verse":13,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"text","text":" I am the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" your God who set you apart from the peoples. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ex 3:8","book":"Exo","chapter":3,"verse":8},{"label":"Ex 13:5","book":"Exo","chapter":13,"verse":5},{"label":"Nm 14:8","book":"Num","chapter":14,"verse":8},{"label":"Nm 16:13–14","book":"Num","chapter":16,"verse":13}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Lev:20:25","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Therefore you are to distinguish the clean animal from the unclean one, and the unclean bird from the clean one. Do not become contaminated "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Dt 7:26","book":"Deu","chapter":7,"verse":26,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" by any land animal, bird, or whatever crawls on the ground; I have set these apart as unclean for you. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lv 11:1","book":"Lev","chapter":11,"verse":1,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Dt 7:26","book":"Deu","chapter":7,"verse":26},{"label":"Lv 11:1","book":"Lev","chapter":11,"verse":1}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Lev:20:26","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"You are to be holy to me because I, the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":", am holy, and I have set you apart from the nations to be mine. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ex 19:5–6","book":"Exo","chapter":19,"verse":5,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lv 11:44","book":"Lev","chapter":11,"verse":44,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 1:4","book":"Isa","chapter":1,"verse":4,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 6:3","book":"Isa","chapter":6,"verse":3,"letter":"d"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ex 19:5–6","book":"Exo","chapter":19,"verse":5},{"label":"Lv 11:44","book":"Lev","chapter":11,"verse":44},{"label":"Is 1:4","book":"Isa","chapter":1,"verse":4},{"label":"Is 6:3","book":"Isa","chapter":6,"verse":3}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Lev:20:27","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"“A man or a woman who is "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Lit is in them"},{"kind":"text","text":" a medium or a spiritist must be put to death. They are to be stoned; their death is their own fault.”"}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Lit is in them"}]}]},"cachedAt":1783279337207}